compiz: compiz ( OpenGL window and compositing manager)
compiz:
compiz: Compiz is one of the first OpenGL-accelerated compositing window
compiz: managers for the X Window System. The integration allows it to perform
compiz: compositing effects in window management, such as a minimization
compiz: effect and a cube workspace.  Compiz is an OpenGL compositing manager
compiz: that use Compiz use EXT_texture_from_pixmap OpenGL extension extension
compiz: for binding redirected top-level windows to texture objects.
compiz:
compiz: http://www.go-compiz.org
